 (322&#x02013;332) track inequities in ownership of mosquito nets. </p></sec></sec><sec><title>Zambia</title><sec><title>Seeking care in rural areas</title><p>Karsten Lunze et al. (333&#x02013;342) assess the quality of care provided to children presenting with fever.</p></sec></sec><sec><title>Global</title><sec><title>Preventing obesity and malnutrition</title><p>H&#x000e9;l&#x000e8;ne Delisle et al. (385&#x02013;388) argue that more nutritionists are needed.</p></sec><sec><title>Measuring quality of care</title><p>Johanna Hanefeld et al. (368&#x02013;374) list problems and solutions for low- and middle-income countries.</p></sec></sec></body></article>